Homepage: https://github.com/amd989/infrafi

Package: infrafid
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: network-manager | wpasupplicant
Description: InfraFi IR WiFi credential receiver daemon
 Receives WiFi credentials transmitted via infrared (RC-6 protocol)
 from a Flipper Zero running the InfraFi app. Automatically connects
 to the transmitted WiFi network using NetworkManager, systemd-networkd,
 or ifupdown.
 .
 Designed for headless Linux servers with CIR (Consumer IR) receivers
 such as the ITE8708 found in Intel NUCs.
